<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-19 03:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1937 &Cx1f; ttd-z
r a BC-SC-CHANGES-1STLD-WRIT     02-19 0988
