<SLUG> BC-MARRIAGE-STRESS-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
WHEN IT PAYS TO ARGUE WITH A SPOUSE 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
special arrangement only. Asian and European points: contact Karl
Horwitz in Paris for details and prices (Phone: 47 42 17 11; FAX:
47-42-80-44). Latin American points: contact the Los Angeles office
(Phone: 310-996-0075; FAX: 310-996-0089) 
(bl) 
 By ERIC NAGOURNEY   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   There are those who may think it is something out of an Edward
Albee play, or maybe ``The Newlywed Game'' meets Jerry Springer.
But for the couple tired of flowers, chocolates and renting Nora
Ephron films, it could just be another way to celebrate their love.
