<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-19 19:47 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2281 &Cx1f; tta-z
u p BC-SC-REPUBS-ASSESS-NYT &LR;      02-19 1119
