   &UR; ADVICE, HOW-TO AND MISCELLANEOUS &LR;
</P>
<P>
   1. RELATIONSHIP RESCUE, by Phillip C. McGraw.
</P>
<P>
   (Hyperion, $22.95.) A seven-step program for reconnecting
</P>
<P>
   with one's partner. (b)
</P>
<P>
   2. WHO MOVED MY CHEESE? by Spencer Johnson. (Putnam,
</P>
<P>
   $19.95.) How to deal with changes at work and in life
</P>
<P>
   in general. (b)
</P>
<P>
   3. BODY FOR LIFE, by Bill Phillips with Michael D'Orso.
</P>
<P>
   (HarperCollins, $26.) Ways to improve one's body and
</P>
<P>
   one's life. (b)
</P>
<P>
   4. DON'T SWEAT THE SMALL STUFF IN LOVE, by Richard
</P>
<P>
   Carlson and Kristine Carlson. (Hyperion, $15.95.)
</P>
<P>
   Ways to maintain good personal relationships.
</P>
